Security MCP Server
Copyright (c) 2025

This product is an independent project that provides an MCP (Model Context Protocol)
server interface for the Bearer CLI security scanning tool.

IMPORTANT DISCLAIMERS:
- This project is NOT affiliated with, endorsed by, or sponsored by Bearer.
- This is an independent implementation maintained by dapperdivers.
- Bearer CLI is a separate product with its own licensing and terms.

Third-party Software:
This software uses the following third-party tools:
- Bearer CLI (https://github.com/Bearer/bearer) - Security scanning tool
  Licensed under its own terms (see Bearer's repository for details)
- Python and various Python packages (see requirements.txt)

For questions about this MCP server, please contact:
- GitHub: https://github.com/dapperdivers/security_mcp
- Issues: https://github.com/dapperdivers/security_mcp/issues

For questions about Bearer CLI itself, please refer to:
- Bearer Documentation: https://docs.bearer.com
- Bearer GitHub: https://github.com/Bearer/bearer